  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715010/extras/978f88d5c8012217906056b0ec583cbb.poster.avif?t=1745903701\" width=616 height=32 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715010/extras/978f88d5c8012217906056b0ec583cbb.webm?t=1745903701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715010/extras/978f88d5c8012217906056b0ec583cbb.mp4?t=1745903701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Diamo XL</strong> is a fast-paced, arcade-style score chaser where survival means constantly moving and adapting. Navigate all zones around the diamond, collect points before enemies destroy them, and don't stop moving to maintain your multiplier for high scores. Fill in all four triangles to complete the diamond and earn bonus points!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715010/extras/00c381fd3a306cee690824cc4c49ef53.poster.avif?t=1745903701\" width=616 height=32 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715010/extras/00c381fd3a306cee690824cc4c49ef53.webm?t=1745903701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715010/extras/00c381fd3a306cee690824cc4c49ef53.mp4?t=1745903701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Simple & Intuitive Controls</strong> – Play using keyboard (Arrow Keys/WASD), controller (D-Pad/Joystick), or mouse clicks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fast-Paced Arcade Gameplay</strong> – Endless action that ramps up in difficulty.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlockable Characters</strong> – Complete challenges to play as unique characters with different stats.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Score Tracking & Multipliers</strong> – Improve and perfect your high score strategy.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam Integration</strong> – Achievements, Leaderboards, Trading Cards, Cloud Saves.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bite-Sized & Addictive</strong> – Perfect for quick sessions between other games.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Uniquely Crafted Audio</strong> – Sound effects made using my own voice and royalty-free audio and Royalty Free Music from Bensound called \"Moose\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715010/extras/275435c6dec6b8c5b04fadf6674a28a5.poster.avif?t=1745903701\" width=616 height=32 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715010/extras/275435c6dec6b8c5b04fadf6674a28a5.webm?t=1745903701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715010/extras/275435c6dec6b8c5b04fadf6674a28a5.mp4?t=1745903701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Diamo XL is a simple yet rewarding arcade game focused on high scores and replayability. I appreciate all feedback and will continue supporting the game. Feel free to reach out via Discord or my website if you have suggestions or want to say hi.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thanks for checking it out, I hope you enjoy playing!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Adam Nickerson – Adamvision Studios</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715010/extras/978f88d5c8012217906056b0ec583cbb.poster.avif?t=1745903701\" width=616 height=32 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715010/extras/978f88d5c8012217906056b0ec583cbb.webm?t=1745903701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715010/extras/978f88d5c8012217906056b0ec583cbb.mp4?t=1745903701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Diamo XL</strong> is a fast-paced, arcade-style score chaser where survival means constantly moving and adapting. Navigate all zones around the diamond, collect points before enemies destroy them, and don't stop moving to maintain your multiplier for high scores. Fill in all four triangles to complete the diamond and earn bonus points!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715010/extras/00c381fd3a306cee690824cc4c49ef53.poster.avif?t=1745903701\" width=616 height=32 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715010/extras/00c381fd3a306cee690824cc4c49ef53.webm?t=1745903701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715010/extras/00c381fd3a306cee690824cc4c49ef53.mp4?t=1745903701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Simple & Intuitive Controls</strong> – Play using keyboard (Arrow Keys/WASD), controller (D-Pad/Joystick), or mouse clicks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fast-Paced Arcade Gameplay</strong> – Endless action that ramps up in difficulty.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlockable Characters</strong> – Complete challenges to play as unique characters with different stats.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Score Tracking & Multipliers</strong> – Improve and perfect your high score strategy.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam Integration</strong> – Achievements, Leaderboards, Trading Cards, Cloud Saves.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bite-Sized & Addictive</strong> – Perfect for quick sessions between other games.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Uniquely Crafted Audio</strong> – Sound effects made using my own voice and royalty-free audio and Royalty Free Music from Bensound called \"Moose\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715010/extras/275435c6dec6b8c5b04fadf6674a28a5.poster.avif?t=1745903701\" width=616 height=32 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715010/extras/275435c6dec6b8c5b04fadf6674a28a5.webm?t=1745903701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/715010/extras/275435c6dec6b8c5b04fadf6674a28a5.mp4?t=1745903701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Diamo XL is a simple yet rewarding arcade game focused on high scores and replayability. I appreciate all feedback and will continue supporting the game. Feel free to reach out via Discord or my website if you have suggestions or want to say hi.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thanks for checking it out, I hope you enjoy playing!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Adam Nickerson – Adamvision Studios</strong></p>",
